<br>
Oh yeah and where does it drop? I've seen it drop in Skyfire, woudln't surprise me to see it in  seb as well. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=etudar>Etudar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/2/01 10:07:25 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.nerv-un.net/~black/images/smalletudar.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Plainsight</span><hr size=1> Got mine in SF <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugosifosiol.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gosifosiol</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/10/01 4:24:11 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Plainsight</span><hr size=1> if you got Sage's Bracelet/Sorcerer's Wristband/Bangle of the Invoker/Icicle Bracelet, then theres no real need of this spell right... since it got chill sight as effect. <p><center> 
